00:00:26.996 --> 00:00:29.216
&gt;&gt;Narrator: But another group
of Fremont students spends their

00:00:29.216 --> 00:00:31.596
after school hours
doing community service

00:00:31.596 --> 00:00:33.466
and running small business ventures.

00:00:33.916 --> 00:00:37.036
And this year, their diligence
carried them into the finals

00:00:37.036 --> 00:00:40.076
of a competition for the best
high school business program

00:00:40.076 --> 00:00:40.816
in the country.

00:00:41.086 --> 00:00:43.666
